TRW Inc, responding to allegations byan ex-employee that it was unethical in defense contractdealings, said it had previously informed the government of thebilling problems.    "We heard nothing of substance as far as allegations byformer employees that were not related to findings that we hadreported to the government of misdeeds at our compressorcomponents group," a TRW spokesman said.     The spokesman said the company conducted an internalinvestigation and presented the findings to the governmentbeginning in late 1984. Reuter&#3;